object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS 
(
    -- current batch query
      SELECT 
          MAX(batch_id) as batch_id
      FROM operations.batch_load_summary
      WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
        AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	    AND target_schema_name = 'silver'
),
agent as
(
    --agent query
    SELECT DISTINCT
        'ADM' as provider_termination_source_system,
        'Agency' as provider_termination_domain,
        DECODE(tg.type,'A','Agency','P','Producer',NULL) as provider_termination_type,
        ISNULL(tg.originating_source_name,NULL) as originating_source_name,
        ISNULL(tg.originating_load_type,NULL) as originating_load_type,
        ISNULL(tg.adm_termination_guidewire_row_status,NULL) as provider_termination_row_status,
        ISNULL(tg.id,NULL) as provider_termination_row_source_system_key,
        ISNULL(CAST(ta.agency_num AS integer),NULL) as tac_provider_code,
        ISNULL(ta.agency_num,NULL) as acx_provider_code,
        ISNULL(tg.sub_code,NULL) as tac_sub_provider_code,
        DECODE(tg.sub_code,NULL,NULL,'Agency') as tac_sub_provider_type,
        ISNULL(tg.state,NULL) as provider_license_issued_in_state_alpha_2_code,
        al.company_provider_was_appointed_to as company_provider_was_appointed_to,
        DECODE(tg.effective_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.effective_date) as provider_transfer_effective_date,
        DECODE(tg.new_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.new_date) as new_business_can_no_longer_be_written_by_provider_date,
        DECODE(tg.renewal_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.renewal_date) as business_can_no_longer_be_renewed_under_provider_date,
        ISNULL(tg.replaced_by,NULL) as provider_code_which_terminated_provider_was_merged_into,
        ISNULL(tg.term_type,NULL) as termination_type_code_for_cratchit,
        DECODE(tg.term_type,'L','L - License Termination','A','A - Appointment Termination',NULL) as termination_type_description_for_cratchit,
        ISNULL(tg.term_reason_code,NULL,NULL,tg.term_reason_code) as termination_reason_code_for_cratchit,
        DECODE(tg.term_reason_code,'1','1 - Voluntary Termination','11','11 - Appointed in Error','14','14 - Company Merger', NULL) as termination_reason_description_for_cratchit,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%BOP%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_businessowners_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%HO%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_homeowners_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%DP%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_dwelling_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%BOPU%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_commercial_umbrella_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%PUL%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_personal_umbrella_indicator,
        ISNULL(tg.noticeto_agent,NULL) as notice_of_termination_sent_to_agent_indicator,
        ISNULL(tg.created,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as provider_termination_source_system_created_datetime,
        ISNULL(tg.modified,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as provider_termination_source_system_modified_datetime
    FROM bronze.adm_termination_guidewire tg
    LEFT JOIN bronze.adm_t_agency ta
        ON tg.agency_nup = ta.agency_nup
    LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT agency_id, term_id, DECODE(bs_appointed_date, NULL,NULL,'Bay State') as company_provider_was_appointed_to  
    from  bronze.adm_agency_license al_in 
    union all 
    SELECT agency_id, term_id, DECODE(ca_appointed_date,NULL,NULL,'Cambridge Mutual') as company_provider_was_appointed_to  
    from  bronze.adm_agency_license al_in 
    union all
    SELECT agency_id, term_id, DECODE(mk_appointed_date,NULL,NULL, 'Merrimack Mutual') as company_provider_was_appointed_to  
    from  bronze.adm_agency_license al_in 
    )al
        ON ta.agency_nup = al.agency_id
            AND tg.id = al.term_id
    WHERE tg.type = 'A'
    AND adm_t_agency_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
    AND adm_termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
),
producer as
(
    -- producer query
    SELECT DISTINCT
        'ADM' as provider_termination_source_system,
        'Agency' as provider_termination_domain,
        DECODE(tg.type,'A','Agency','P','Producer',NULL) as provider_termination_type,
        ISNULL(tg.originating_source_name,NULL) as originating_source_name,
        ISNULL(tg.originating_load_type,NULL) as originating_load_type,
        ISNULL(tg.adm_termination_guidewire_row_status,NULL) as provider_termination_row_status,
        ISNULL(tg.id,NULL) as provider_termination_row_source_system_key,
        ISNULL(pl.producer_id,NULL) as tac_provider_code,
        ISNULL(tg.gw_producer_id,NULL) as acx_provider_code,
        ISNULL(tg.sub_code,NULL) as tac_sub_provider_code,
        DECODE(tg.sub_code,NULL,NULL,'Producer') as tac_sub_provider_type,
        ISNULL(tg.state,NULL) as provider_license_issued_in_state_alpha_2_code,
        ISNULL(pl.company,NULL) as company_provider_was_appointed_to,
        DECODE(tg.effective_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.effective_date) as provider_transfer_effective_date,
        DECODE(tg.new_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.new_date) as new_business_can_no_longer_be_written_by_provider_date,
        DECODE(tg.renewal_date,NULL,'1900-01-01',tg.renewal_date) as business_can_no_longer_be_renewed_under_provider_date,
        ISNULL(tg.replaced_by,NULL) as provider_code_which_terminated_provider_was_merged_into,
        ISNULL(tg.term_type,NULL) as termination_type_code_for_cratchit,
        DECODE(tg.term_type,'L','L - License Termination','A','A - Appointment Termination',NULL) as termination_type_description_for_cratchit,
        ISNULL(tg.term_reason_code,NULL) as termination_reason_code_for_cratchit,
        DECODE(tg.term_reason_code,'1','1 - Voluntary Termination','11','11 - Appointed in Error','14','14 - Company Merger', NULL) 
        as termination_reason_description_for_cratchit,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%BOP%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_businessowners_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%HO%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_homeowners_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%DP%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_dwelling_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%BOPU%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_commercial_umbrella_indicator,
        (CASE WHEN LEN(TRIM(tg.lob)) = 0 THEN 'NULL'
                WHEN upper(tg.lob) like '%PUL%' THEN 'YES'
                ELSE 'NO' END) as terminated_provider_to_personal_umbrella_indicator,
        ISNULL(tg.noticeto_agent,NULL) as notice_of_termination_sent_to_agent_indicator,
        ISNULL(tg.created,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as provider_termination_source_system_created_datetime,
        ISNULL(tg.modified,'1900-01-01 00:00:00') as provider_termination_source_system_modified_datetime
    FROM bronze.adm_termination_guidewire tg
    LEFT JOIN bronze.adm_producer_license pl
    on  tg.gw_producer_id = pl.gw_producer_id
        AND tg.id = pl.term_id
        WHERE pl.term_id <> 0
        AND pl.term_id IS NOT NULL
        AND tg.type = 'P'
    AND pl.adm_producer_license_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
    AND tg.adm_termination_guidewire_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000000'
),
agent_producer_union as
(
    -- agent producer union query
    select * from agent union select * from producer
),
tgt as 
(
	-- target lookup query
	select
		provider_termination_id as tgt_provider_termination_id,
		provider_termination_row_source_system_key as tgt_provider_termination_row_source_system_key,
		provider_termination_row_md5checksum as tgt_provider_termination_row_md5checksum
	from
		silver.provider_terminations
)
-- final select query
select 
	current_batch.batch_id, 
	agent_producer_union.*,
	tgt.*
from agent_producer_union
left join tgt on agent_producer_union.provider_termination_row_source_system_key = tgt.tgt_provider_termination_row_source_system_key
cross join current_batch;
